    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I have a local WIP branch that gets rid of `IDisable` on power-related traits (`RequiresPower` and `CanPowerDown`) which should bring us a good deal closer to that, as the other remaining usages of `IDisable` seem individually trivial in comparison.*\r\n\r\n*Of course there might still be some implicit dependencies I'm not aware of."
